text: They are so friendly, bought Mandarin orange then the cashier purposely come to help me check whether they are spoilt, appreciate it!

Four self-checkout kiosks; only one cashier. Four tables with eight seats outside. Convenient machine ‘i.Jooz’ only S$2 for a cup of freshly squeezed orange juice next to trolleys (salon & florist shops)
Nutrisoy new limited edition soya milk really nice leh!

Take a look at the photos.  Fruits on display are overriped and some are not replenished although this is a 24 hr outlet. Some items are also without price tag.  This situation is quite frequent.  Need to improve.

Will have most of household needs. Best to go off-peak, only one cashier counter open most of the time, self checkout is chaotic. Not organised bcos of limited space/resources allocated for checking out.
